      • findRatingAndSetReview

        private java.lang.String findRatingAndSetReview()
        This is will read the rating and reviews from the Review database to calculate the general user rating. During the process, the stringlized reviews will be appended to this.review as well.
        Returns:
        the calculated overall user rating scores, e.g. 4.5; Note that if there is less than one review, 'N.A.' will be returned instead
